Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.33,0:00:05.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這片寂靜撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.50,0:00:11.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領整個世界\N來到熾熱之焰的最深處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.85,0:00:23.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神Zwei
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.85,0:00:32.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的誓言\N灌注在朝天高舉的憤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.03,0:00:35.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度點燃你的熱情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.06,0:00:41.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸騰不已的火紅熱血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.04,0:00:48.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都已無法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.71,0:00:54.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓一片黑暗的明天\N燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.12,0:01:00.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍衛弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.69,0:01:02.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.03,0:01:14.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無畏懼的向前奔馳吧\N直到衝過那深紅色的終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.14,0:01:23.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最後一刻燃盡一切吧\N超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.13,0:01:48.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一場失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是一切的開端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.44,0:01:58.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離超重皇的開發...250年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.88,0:02:06.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離原創.超重機組的誕生...\N又再隔了50年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.26,0:02:11.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.69,0:02:15.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是地球之盾的\N神機超重神潰敗時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.00,0:02:17.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以覺醒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.13,0:02:22.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為這星球之劍而戰鬥的\N完全攻擊用機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.64,0:02:25.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重機組的完成\N又是200年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是漫長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.05,0:02:35.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「創星機」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.09,0:02:39.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決戰的時刻來臨了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.69,0:02:44.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神將成為守護地球之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.23,0:02:47.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝著外星異種的大本營\N豪魔飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.63,0:02:51.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我們也到了\N面對最後一役的時刻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.87,0:02:55.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於那些沒有人心的異星機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.34,0:02:57.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕不屈服!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們地球人的心結合在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.51,0:03:03.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝著有我們的重力勇者\N在奮戰著的天際
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.81,0:03:06.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的希望與祈禱\N都傳送過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.19,0:03:18.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好嚇人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.16,0:03:19.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘依露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.26,0:03:21.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快把豪魔的預測行進路線算出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.00,0:03:26.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保修班朵莉雅班長\N機組各機調整完成了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經全都沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.47,0:03:32.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系統的調整也相當完美...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.28,0:03:34.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊那傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.38,0:03:36.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過塗裝不是用\N多元半導塗料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.58,0:03:39.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是用流線氙合成塗料嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每隔一小時請務必確認一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.25,0:03:45.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且要做好資料哦還有就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.53,0:03:59.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這座城...居然是艘宇宙船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼他也打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這次當做最後一戰了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.97,0:04:06.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真是了不起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.81,0:04:10.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管我還沒有\N他就是我父親的那種感覺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我那個時候...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.32,0:04:14.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不要緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.95,0:04:17.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要說的我都明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.82,0:04:21.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我...並不是孤獨一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.46,0:04:23.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.86,0:04:25.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.06,0:04:28.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經和桑德曼有個約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.56,0:04:32.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要變強要保護地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.70,0:04:36.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要為了沒有武力的人們\N成為奮戰的獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.94,0:04:41.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是英司和大家讓我想起這件事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.78,0:04:44.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一定會守護住這顆星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美的星球啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.72,0:04:52.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像能理解\N父親為什麼會選上這個星球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.13,0:05:04.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.37,0:05:07.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳呆呆的站在這裡\N是在幹嘛啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這和你沒關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇什麼兇嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還擔心\N妳是不是已經嚇傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.04,0:05:17.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你管~嚇壞的人不是你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰嚇壞了呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...她在笑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.06,0:05:31.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露正和斗牙看著同樣的景色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.13,0:05:34.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我到不了的地方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.13,0:05:39.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經到決戰前夕了\N就打起精神繼續戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.35,0:05:51.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.22,0:05:57.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒這樣了呢\N我們能再像這樣子獨處...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會回來這件事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.69,0:06:04.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是不是早就猜到啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.56,0:06:07.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月.立花\N絕不是個在戰鬥之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.96,0:06:10.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就獨自逃跑的女人不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.57,0:06:13.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就當做這是在恭維我囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.40,0:06:17.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是對於待過EFA情報部這點\N我可是不會後悔的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.97,0:06:21.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那對我來說\N是一條必須選擇的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.74,0:06:24.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須選擇的路...是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.65,0:06:29.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳...保持這樣子真的好嗎\N雷文?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.89,0:06:34.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不要事後後悔\N所以決定和他一起走下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.26,0:06:36.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我所選擇的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.23,0:06:41.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是一樣啊\N這麼拙於表達自己...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.80,0:06:49.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要用憎恨悲傷鮮血和破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.17,0:06:51.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血洗並毀滅這顆星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.21,0:06:53.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.92,0:07:09.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼從超乎我所能想像的\N久遠以前就一直戰鬥著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是為了守護這個世界...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我的戰爭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.80,0:07:17.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是為了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.27,0:07:19.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓那個人回過頭來看看我而已...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.47,0:07:24.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長有出擊命令喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.78,0:07:31.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還在心煩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.75,0:07:33.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯中尉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.45,0:07:37.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾經...\N有過覺得自己很渺小的感覺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種念頭隨時都會有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.36,0:07:45.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和這片天空相比的話\N我們的存在真的太渺小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.03,0:07:49.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不能成為\N像超重神那樣子的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.53,0:07:53.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為是我們才能辦到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管後方支援還是其他事\N我們都去做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.67,0:07:59.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為守護好這個地球\N就是我們的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說是不是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.44,0:08:06.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒想到\N會有讓你說教的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯中尉\N超重騎警準備出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.88,0:08:10.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動作快!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.69,0:08:11.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長...天空突然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.69,0:08:17.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偵測到大規模的重力異常!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豪魔開始活動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.31,0:08:35.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是外殼部分\N以現在的速度繼續展開的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.64,0:08:40.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預計20個小時後\N就會包裹住整個地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.12,0:08:45.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是想將地球...整個吞掉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,創星機...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.89,0:08:53.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能以重力子產生的時空歪曲\N把被吞入的行星環境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.83,0:08:56.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新改造為原始時代的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.30,0:09:01.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換言之就是重製星球的裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.37,0:09:05.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球上現存的所有生命\N將會被完全毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.78,0:09:16.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是讓這艘宇宙戰艦燃燒殆盡\N也一定要死守住地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.45,0:09:19.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子防護罩最大出力展開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.86,0:09:27.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了防禦來自豪魔的衝擊波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.93,0:09:30.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力巨星無法離開現在的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.53,0:09:35.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以烈陽超重神侵入豪魔內部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將其擊潰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們上吧斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯英司!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.85,0:09:52.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動炎皇合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.72,0:09:53.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.99,0:09:57.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學型態!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.77,0:10:05.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炎皇合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,降臨!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.45,0:10:28.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炎皇合神.烈陽超重神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.83,0:10:35.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別來礙事啦你們這些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重加農!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.34,0:10:45.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動作...真是靈敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.21,0:10:48.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說不打算就這樣\N放我們過去是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是拖延戰術嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那由我出擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.68,0:10:59.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重翔腕碎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.07,0:11:13.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪到我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.10,0:11:18.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重翔滅鑽炎爆!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.49,0:11:40.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!\N就快要沒有時間了還...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.23,0:11:49.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給我們吧\N你們快前進烈陽超重神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.97,0:11:54.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重騎警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.38,0:11:56.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們還挺行的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.45,0:12:01.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想找機會\N說說看這種台詞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯中尉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.49,0:12:08.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡由我們來擋著\N烈陽超重神快往豪魔去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.76,0:12:11.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點啊斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.16,0:12:15.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解\N妳要小心啊飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.37,0:12:20.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊陣列Z預備!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.44,0:12:24.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星辰群光出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.06,0:12:45.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方本體開始更加擴大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.13,0:12:48.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力異常程度持續增加中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.13,0:12:50.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.23,0:12:52.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請快一點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎的勇者們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.14,0:13:05.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為會很盛大的歡迎我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.58,0:13:08.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直像是...沒有任何人在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行進方向出現高能源反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是類似動力爐的物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能中止那個的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.19,0:13:22.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大量殺戮機的豪魔攻擊\N就會停止了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.16,0:13:26.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我們放手把它給轟爛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.82,0:13:42.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.82,0:13:45.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎蒞臨我的城堡.豪魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.02,0:13:49.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓行星燃燒毀滅的太陽\N烈陽超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.99,0:13:54.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及我的小舅子.疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.27,0:14:02.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要縮在那個地方\N快過來我這裡嘛疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也想和我作個了斷吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.38,0:14:13.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再拖拖拉拉的話\N你心愛的星球就會被吞噬掉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.85,0:14:16.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些污穢人類與被破壞的大自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.68,0:14:19.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都會徹底淨化的乾乾淨淨喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.16,0:14:27.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你那什麼創星機比起來\N效率可是好到你們無法想像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.03,0:14:30.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀舅舅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.77,0:14:32.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露妳不要緊吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.40,0:14:37.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還好\N如果他真的是修紀舅舅的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.47,0:14:39.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要阻止他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.27,0:14:43.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快來吧疾克\N快到我的面前來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.78,0:14:45.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這死老頭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們被他困住了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.73,0:15:00.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.13,0:15:05.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是個陷阱\N你怎麼能接受那樣的挑釁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.74,0:15:11.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你原本所擁有的G因子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.41,0:15:14.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為轉換成\N永久新陳代謝機能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才有現在這個不死的肉體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.15,0:15:19.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你搭上這機體就表示...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.45,0:15:23.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要讓G因子復活\N並失去這個不死的肉體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的願意這麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次我非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.39,0:15:31.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.44,0:15:47.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答應我疾克\N答應我你一定會回來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.64,0:15:49.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.98,0:15:59.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重Σ 準備出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.45,0:17:07.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.06,0:17:10.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神機Σ超重神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:19.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電光雷管!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.41,0:17:30.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還剩最後一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.72,0:17:44.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力放射鏢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.43,0:17:52.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神機超重神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重騎槍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.55,0:18:45.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重粉碎斷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.76,0:18:56.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.97,0:19:05.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰將的諸位各位沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.91,0:19:11.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦的應戰\N真是太感謝各位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.22,0:19:16.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請和我握手好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.29,0:19:27.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳變強了...而且也變得更美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.97,0:19:39.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.75,0:19:49.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,復仇的時刻到了露菲拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.91,0:20:16.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.91,0:20:20.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼東西啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.95,0:20:24.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方似乎是\N超高密度的能源聚合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.75,0:20:27.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源的總量...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.15,0:20:30.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎是...行星的兩倍多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑟力亞斯與蘭比亞斯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.13,0:20:35.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說\N把兩顆星球毀滅時的能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都封印在那裡面了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.60,0:20:41.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這群頑強抵抗的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.24,0:20:44.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是來自我故鄉的嘆息之炎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.31,0:20:47.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與魂魄的慟哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.27,0:20:50.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們就好好的親身體會一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.66,0:21:09.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露菲拉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露菲拉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.42,0:21:34.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露菲拉...對不起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.03,0:21:42.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是打算謝罪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀...大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.70,0:21:49.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是你\N為罪行付出代價的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.07,0:21:51.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.54,0:22:03.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因熱戀而無法成眠的夜晚\N已經看膩了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.88,0:22:11.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要聽到人的聲音\N所以隨意打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.49,0:22:20.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了靠不住的語音留言\N你現在到底在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.00,0:22:28.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映著冰箱內的燈光\N我在狹小的宇宙裡彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.81,0:22:37.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我的唱片\N唱針已經跳開不知幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.32,0:22:44.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信這不變的溫度\N一直到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.73,0:22:46.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.33,0:22:52.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.43,0:22:55.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們手牽著手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.10,0:23:03.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N淺淺呼吸籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.41,0:23:10.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.28,0:23:12.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們閉上雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.39,0:23:21.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜進你夢裡的\N甜美節奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.57,0:23:29.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一刻終於到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.54,0:23:30.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.64,0:23:32.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等這一刻等到心力憔悴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.34,0:23:34.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸您想說的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.34,0:23:36.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要為這宿命的戰爭劃下休止符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.78,0:23:38.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗清我的所有罪孽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.68,0:23:42.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並將美麗的未來\N託付給你們這些年青人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.75,0:23:44.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不可以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.72,0:23:48.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回最終回\N「魂之凱歌」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.52,0:23:50.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔那多斯(死神)在呼喚我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.29,0:23:52.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去吧莉露...


